DIGEST
SB 49 Engrossed 2026 Regular Session Seabaugh
Present law provides a list of offices that are included in party primary elections.
Proposed law removes the State Board of Elementary and Secondary Education from the list
of offices that are included in party primary elections.
Effective August 1, 2026.
(Amends R.S. 18:2(9))
